        <updateDate>2014-07-31T13:06:18Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Helping Veterans Save for Health Care Act of 2014 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to&nbsp;provide that a veteran receiving hospital care or medical services for a service-connected disabililty is not disqualified from participating in or contributing to a tax-preferred health savings account (HSA). </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
